          "Powder_Feed_Rate_g_min": 5.4
        }
      },
      "Microstructure_Info": {
        "Microstructure_Text": {
          "original": "CoCrNi alloy exhibits single FCC phase. ABF-STEM image shows round-shaped chromium oxide nanoparticles distributed sporadically. SAED confirms FCC phase. EDS mapping shows no elemental segregation, nanoparticles depleted in Co and Ni, rich in O and Cr. Dislocation density after deformation reaches high values.",
          "simplified": "Single FCC phase with dispersed Cr-rich oxide nanoparticles."
        },
